        <p><u><b><font size="+2">System Requirement</font></b></u></p><br />
        <p><b>Hardware requirements:</b></p>
        <ul type="disc">
          <li>512 MB RAM, 1.8 GHz or faster Processor, 20 GB Hard Disk with atleast 500 MB free in Primary Drive (usually C Drive)<br />
        <li>Screen resolution of 1024X768 or more.</li>
		<li>Decent quality speakers/headphones to listen to the audio. Make sure to turn them on with a volume through which the audio is clearly audible and understandable.</li>
        <li>56 kbps or faster internet connection.</li>
        </ul>
        
          <p><b>Software requirements:</b></p>
        
         <ul type="disc">
          <li>Audio drivers/ software for the audio to be played. <br />
        <li>Microsoft Word or any similar application to open .doc files.</li>
		<li>Any PDF (Portable Document Format) reader such as Adobe Reader etc.</li>
        <li>Adobe Flash player 10 or later</li>
        <li>Internet Explorer 5 or later, Opera 9 or later, Google Chrome 8 or later, Mozilla Firefox 3 or later or other similar browser which supports Adobe Flash 10.</li>
        <li>Windows XP Service Pack 2 or later, Windows Vista or Windows 7 or similar operating systems which support the other softwares listed above.</li>
        </ul>
        
